    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "520589_62_2018-2032",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "2018-2032",
      "markText": "感受被看到，就是最好的治疗。",
      "totalCount": 9282,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=520589&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=2018&rangeEnd=2032",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7df32f2057f18d7df6bb550?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=2018&rangeEnd=2032"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "520589_81_2839-2901",
      "chapterUid": 81,
      "range": "2839-2901",
      "markText": "人生由几百、几千乃至几万个大大小小的选择构成，等你老了，回顾一生的时候，你发现最亏待的，恰恰是你自己，那你这一生，就白活了。",
      "totalCount": 6544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=520589&chapterUid=81&rangeStart=2839&rangeEnd=2901",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7df32f2057f18d7df6bb550?chapterUid=81&rangeStart=2839&rangeEnd=2901"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "520589_55_4590-4664",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "4590-4664",
      "markText": "不要让他人的观点所发出的噪音淹没你内心的声音。最为重要的是，要有遵从你的内心和直觉的勇气，它们可能已知道你想成为一个什么样的人。其他事物都是次要的。",
      "totalCount": 6135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=520589&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=4590&rangeEnd=4664",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7df32f2057f18d7df6bb550?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=4590&rangeEnd=4664"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "520589_65_4585-4625",
      "chapterUid": 65,
      "range": "4585-4625",
      "markText": "成熟的父母不会在第一时间去处理孩子的问题，他们会先处理孩子的感受。",
      "totalCount": 5888,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=520589&chapterUid=65&rangeStart=4585&rangeEnd=4625",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7df32f2057f18d7df6bb550?chapterUid=65&rangeStart=4585&rangeEnd=4625"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "520589_54_4267-4343",
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "range": "4267-4343",
      "markText": "同情心有两种。一种是对弱者的可怜，但内心同时有一种我很好很强大的自恋。另一种是共情，即，我深深地碰触到了你的感受，进入到了你的世界，感你所感，想你所想。",
      "totalCount": 5334,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=520589&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=4267&rangeEnd=4343",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7df32f2057f18d7df6bb550?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=4267&rangeEnd=4343"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "520589_48_8895-8943",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "8895-8943",
      "markText": "婚姻之所以容易成为爱情的坟墓，一个很重要的原因是，婚姻只是我们过去家庭模式的复制。",
      "totalCount": 5148,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=520589&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=8895&rangeEnd=8943",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7df32f2057f18d7df6bb550?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=8895&rangeEnd=8943"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "520589_50_460-544",
      "chapterUid": 50,
      "range": "460-544",
      "markText": "亲人间的理解之所以很难，关键原因在于，我们习惯从自己的坐标体系出发，去推测、揣摩、评价甚至抨击另一个人，却完全忘了，对方也有一个现象场，有一个与自己完全不同的坐标体系。",
      "totalCount": 5134,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=520589&chapterUid=50&rangeStart=460&rangeEnd=544",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7df32f2057f18d7df6bb550?chapterUid=50&rangeStart=460&rangeEnd=544"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "520589_48_11269-11306",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "11269-11306",
      "markText": "你再亲密的人也是另外一个人，是和我们一样重要、一样独立的人。",
